#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.33:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.33:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga "
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Daṇḍasutta "
msgstr "33. A Stick "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.33:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, daṇḍo uparivehāsaṃ khitto sakimpi mūlena nipatati, sakimpi aggena nipatati; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a stick was tossed up in the air. Sometimes it’d fall on its bottom, sometimes the middle, and sometimes the top. "

#. VAR: taṇhāsaṃyojanā sandhāvantā saṃsarantā → taṇhāsaṃyojanabandhā sandhāvatā (mr)
msgctxt "sn56.33:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, avijjānīvaraṇā sattā taṇhāsaṃyojanā sandhāvantā saṃsarantā sakimpi asmā lokā paraṃ lokaṃ gacchanti, sakimpi parasmā lokā imaṃ lokaṃ āgacchanti. "
msgstr "It’s the same for sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. Sometimes they go from this world to the other world, and sometimes they come from the other world to this world. "

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.4"
msgid "Adiṭṭhattā, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s because they haven’t seen the four noble truths. "

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.5"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.6"
msgid "Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasaccassa. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.440, sc2
msgctxt "sn56.33:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.33:2.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

